OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776881467
OL,3,CMan denies stalking and harassing Jess
OL,4,CPhillips with 'threatening' emails
OL,6,FA man has denied stalking Home Office
OL,7,Fminister Jess Phillips.
OL,9,FLee Owens, 47, is set to face trial
OL,10,Fover a series of threatening and
OL,11,Faggressive emails he is alleged to
OL,12,Fhave sent to the MP for Birmingham
OL,13,FYardley.
OL,15,FAt Cheltenham Magistrates' Court on
OL,16,FTuesday, Owens pleaded not guilty to
OL,17,Fstalking, having previously denied a
OL,18,Fcharge of harassment.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
