CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776881467
OL,3,CMan denies stalking and harassing Jess
OL,4,CPhillips with 'threatening' emails
OL,6,FHe was granted bail under the
OL,7,Fcondition that he does not attempt to
OL,8,Fcontact Ms Phillips.
OL,10,FOwens, of Matson, Gloucester, is
OL,11,Fcharged with harassing Ms Phillips by
OL,12,Fsending her 31 emails between January
OL,13,F22 and January 25 2025.
OL,15,FHe is also accused of sending an
OL,16,Fexcessive volume of aggressive and
OL,17,Fthreatening emails between July 10 and
OL,18,FJuly 14 2025 which caused Ms Phillips
OL,19,Fserious alarm or distress, amounting
OL,20,Fto stalking.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
