PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776881467
OL,3,CMan denies stalking and harassing Jess
OL,4,CPhillips with 'threatening' emails
OL,6,FAddressing Owens, District Judge
OL,7,FNicholas Wattam said: "There are two
OL,8,Fcriminal charges and you've told me
OL,9,Fthat you're not guilty.
OL,11,F"I'm sending your case to the crown
OL,12,Fcourt now."
OL,14,FOwens is due to appear at Gloucester
OL,15,FCrown Court on May 19 for a case
OL,16,Fmanagement hearing.
OL,18,FAnton Doyle appeared for the
OL,19,Fprosecution while Mike Hartnell
OL,20,Frepresented Owens.
